body:
These examples use the following `databases` and `collections`
in the storage configuration:

```json
"databases" : [
  {
    "name": "multiCollDB",
    "collections": [
      {
        "name": "air_airlines",
        "dataSources": [{
          "storeName" : "egS3Store",
          "path" : "egData/air_airlines.json"
        }]
      },
      {
        "name": "airbnb",
        "dataSources": [{
          "storeName" : "sampleS3Store",
          "path" : "json/airbnb/*"
        }]
      },
      {
        "name": "weather",
        "dataSources": [{
          "storeName" : "sampleS3Store",
          "path" : "json/weather/*"
        }]
      }
    ]
  }
]
```
